## How to Use This Document

This spec covers the inputs layer of the Scenario Planner only — from page load through saving a scenario. The comparison section (pressure dashboard, visual analysis, data grid) is a separate pass and is not in scope here.

Read this document fully before writing any code. Section 1 covers layout and structure. Section 2 covers each component in detail. Section 3 covers interaction states and behavior. Section 4 covers the run and save flow. Section 5 covers technical wiring notes.

